---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Rumi
  Translator: Coleman Barks
  Author: Rumi
  ISBN: 978-0060845971
  Publisher: HarperOne
Format: Verse
By: Rumi
Title: The Sun Is Love
Description: March 23
---
The sun is love. The lover,
a speck circling the sun.

A spring wind moves to dance
any branch that isn't dead.
